===Noun===
[[Image:ChampagneCorksLarge.jpg|thumb|Champagne corks (noun sense 2)]]
{{en-noun}}

# {{uncountable}} The bark of the [[cork oak]], which is very light and porous and is very good for making bottle stoppers and insulation material.
# A bottle stopper made from this or any [[other]] material.
#: ''It is hard to call it wine with a straight-face, when the '''cork''' is made of plastic.''

